Anywhere.

01:29:38.638 --> 01:29:40.162
Everywhere.

01:29:40.206 --> 01:29:43.039
Wherever there is evil
to be fought.

01:29:44.644 --> 01:29:47.272
But on lonely nights,

01:29:47.313 --> 01:29:50.339
